if i’m trapped in here!

341
00:13:52,140 --> 00:13:53,480
What am I gonna do?

342
00:13:53,510 --> 00:13:55,810
If it falls into their hands,
it’s all over!

343
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:58,210
♪

344
00:14:01,520 --> 00:14:02,480
Josuke: Huh?

345
00:14:04,250 --> 00:14:06,220
