to keep us from finding it?

347
00:14:08,390 --> 00:14:09,920
Okuyasu: I don’t have
the foggiest clue,

348
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:11,390
but i’m not gonna sweat it.

349
00:14:11,430 --> 00:14:14,930
