371
00:15:00,170 --> 00:15:03,040
Okuyasu: Sounds like you
caught your breath. ( Laughs )

372
00:15:03,080 --> 00:15:05,280
those tacks
ain’t goin’ nowhere, gramps.

373
00:15:05,310 --> 00:15:07,050
Yoshihiro: Tacks, you say?

374
00:15:07,080 --> 00:15:09,420
that must mean
you stuck me to the post.

375
00:15:09,450 --> 00:15:11,190
- ( Both gasp )
- ( Yoshihiro laughs )

376
00:15:11,220 --> 00:15:15,160
What a red-letter day.
You idiots don’t realize it,

