00:20:21,360 --> 00:20:23,560
Blades always
give him razor burn.

493
00:20:23,600 --> 00:20:25,430
- ( Doorbell rings )
- ( Gasps )

494
00:20:25,470 --> 00:20:27,400
Man: Listen, pal!
You still haven’t paid

495
00:20:27,440 --> 00:20:29,400
last month’s rent,
you cheapskate!

496
00:20:29,440 --> 00:20:31,710
Now you owe for this month,
so fork over the yen!

497
00:20:31,740 --> 00:20:33,310
Not leaving ’til i’m paid!

498
00:20:33,340 --> 00:20:34,380
( Shinobu gasps )

499
00:20:34,410 --> 00:20:35,810
Kira: Rent?

500
00:20:37,710 --> 00:20:39,750
Shinobu: You heard the man.
Go and get the money

501
00:20:39,780 --> 00:20:41,480
from the safe
before he kicks us out.

502
00:20:41,520 --> 00:20:43,790
Kira: Right. The safe.

503
00:20:43,820 --> 00:20:46,350
Shinobu: Get a move on!
What are you waiting for?

504
00:20:46,390 --> 00:20:47,790
You have the combination!

505
00:20:47,820 --> 00:20:49,760
( Kira gasping )

506
00:20:51,330 --> 00:20:52,590
( Shinobu gasps )

507
00:20:52,630 --> 00:20:54,730
What are you doing?!
Get back up here!

508
00:20:55,930 --> 00:20:57,570
Kira: Thank you
for taking the time

509
00:20:57,600 --> 00:20:59,500
to drop by this morning,
but I appear

510
00:20:59,530 --> 00:21:01,670
to be running a bit short
on cash at the moment.

511
00:21:01,700 --> 00:21:02,900
I’m sure you understand.

512
00:21:02,940 --> 00:21:04,510
Landlord: Huh?

513
00:21:04,540 --> 00:21:06,910
All that hair gel must be
seeping into your noggin!

514
00:21:06,940 --> 00:21:08,680
I should have known
you young deadbeats

515
00:21:08,710 --> 00:21:10,750
wouldn’t be able to afford
my gorgeous home!

516
00:21:10,780 --> 00:21:13,580
that’s what I get for
doing business with schmucks!

517
00:21:13,620 --> 00:21:15,920
Learn to live
within your means!

518
00:21:15,950 --> 00:21:18,420
Shinobu: You’ll get your money--

519
00:21:18,450 --> 00:21:20,660
kira: No, I think
you misunderstood me earlier.

520
00:21:20,690 --> 00:21:22,520
I said I was short on cash,

521
00:21:22,560 --> 00:21:25,430
but I meant that I only had
a little over 500,000.

522
00:21:25,460 --> 00:21:27,830
- Landlord: Ah!
- ( Shinobu gasps )

523
00:21:27,860 --> 00:21:30,000
Kira: I’ll only be able
to pay for this month,

524
00:21:30,030 --> 00:21:33,070
last month, and for the next
couple of months in advance.

525
00:21:33,100 --> 00:21:34,700
Will that suffice for now?

526
00:21:34,740 --> 00:21:37,110
Landlord: Yes,
that’ll do nicely.

527
00:21:37,140 --> 00:21:39,910
thanks so much.
Have a good one. ( Chuckles )

528
00:21:39,940 --> 00:21:41,940
Until next time.

529
00:21:41,980 --> 00:21:43,580
( Door closes )

530
00:21:43,610 --> 00:21:45,050
Shinobu: Wh-what was that?

531
00:21:46,750 --> 00:21:47,880
I don’t know how,

532
00:21:47,920 --> 00:21:50,390
but you must
have stolen that money.

533
00:21:50,420 --> 00:21:52,450
there’s no point
trying to say that you didn’t.

534
00:21:52,490 --> 00:21:54,960
you stole it from
the landlord’s bag, didn’t you?

535
00:21:56,160 --> 00:21:58,690
if anyone else
was in this situation,

536
00:21:58,730 --> 00:22:01,930
they’d be horrified that their
partner could do such a thing,

537
00:22:01,960 --> 00:22:03,770
but his gusto,

538
00:22:03,800 --> 00:22:06,970
the way he stole the money
and lied about it so easily...

539
00:22:07,000 --> 00:22:09,440
I’ve been with him
for so many years,

540
00:22:09,470 --> 00:22:11,870
but he’s never made me
feel like this before.

541
00:22:11,910 --> 00:22:13,440
It’s exhilarating.

542
00:22:15,610 --> 00:22:19,450
It’s like i’m falling in love
with him for the first time.

543
